&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/QPIDJMS-108&quot; title=&quot;producers don&amp;#39;t correctly handle modified/released delivery state&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;QPIDJMS-108&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;QPIDJMS-108&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Refactoring the AMQP Provider resource management code.&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="14741538" author="jira-bot" created="Fri, 11 Sep 2015 21:08:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit d20986f1e19cdaacf4cc0781263fda189a9932fe in qpid-jms&apos;s branch refs/heads/master from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tabish121&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tabish121&quot;&gt;tabish121&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=qpid-jms.git;h=d20986f&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=qpid-jms.git;h=d20986f&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/QPIDJMS-108&quot; title=&quot;producers don&amp;#39;t correctly handle modified/released delivery state&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;QPIDJMS-108&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;QPIDJMS-108&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Initial fix that adds support for a non-fatal exception that&lt;br/&gt;
propagates to the JmsConnection for dispatch to any registered exception&lt;br/&gt;
listener.  Added tests for the async case to test that the error arrives&lt;br/&gt;
but the connection is not aborted.  Added some handling of Released and&lt;br/&gt;
Modified to the AmqpFixedProducer to fire these errors.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
